com.cloudera.oryx.common.math

Interface Solver


  • public interface Solver
    A solver for the system Ax = b, where A is an n x n matrix and x and b are n-element vectors. An implementation of this class encapsulates a solver which implicitly contains A.
    Author:
    Sean Owen
